            "answer": "<p>We use monk fruit - zero glycemic impact, no digestive side effects, and it doesn't disrupt your gut microbiome. No erythritol, no maltitol, no xylitol.</p><p>Sugar alcohols can cause bloating and may disrupt the beneficial gut bacteria we're trying to feed.</p>"
          }
